Class QNetworkRequest.KnownHeaders

java.lang.Object

      com.trolltech.qt.network.QNetworkRequest.KnownHeaders

Enclosing class:
QNetworkRequest
public static final class QNetworkRequest.KnownHeaders
extends java.lang.Enum
implements QtEnumerator

List of known header types that QNetworkRequest parses. Each known header is also represented in raw form with its full HTTP name.

See also:
header(), setHeader(), rawHeader(), and setRawHeader().

See Also:
Serialized Form
